Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.68,0:00:03.31,Main Dialogue Top,Yua,0,0,0,,Okay, this is episode 9 of the spin-off!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:06.06,Main Dialogue Top,Girl,0,0,0,,We're still doing this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:09.47,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,The Yuriwolf game with nine of \Nour members ended successfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:11.05,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Aoi-chan was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.05,0:00:12.89,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,She totally fooled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:15.20,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,It was a lively recording session, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:17.16,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,It's too bad I didn't get to participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:20.70,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,But it kind of felt like that filled \Nour collaboration quota for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:25.21,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Yeah. Now that that's over, maybe this \Nepisode can sort of give us a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:26.45,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,A dud!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:30.13,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,D-Don't say that when it \Nhasn't even started yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:34.52,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,This pre-title part suddenly feels much \Neasier, too, without the feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.52,0:00:37.67,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,that we have to show all the members \Ninteracting with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.67,0:00:39.47,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's just take it nice and easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:41.89,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Okay, now that the weight is off our shoulders,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:43.56,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,let's go for it again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:18.10,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Did you see that movie on TV last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:18.98,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:20.28,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,I saw it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:22.99,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,It was good, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.42,0:02:24.95,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:27.92,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Sorry, I didn't really see it. I lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.92,0:02:28.79,Main Dialogue,Rin; Yui; Hina; Kanon,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:31.96,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,It was hard to admit that I was \Nthe only one who didn't see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:33.93,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,I know how you feel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:36.71,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Anyway, it really wasn't that interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:37.61,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.61,0:02:39.74,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Yeah! That's what I wanted to talk about!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.74,0:02:41.67,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,It was so boring, I couldn't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:42.26,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:45.65,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,It sounds so interesting! I wish I'd seen it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:47.93,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,No, we're telling you, it was boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:50.41,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Did you see that movie on TV last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:51.72,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Yes, I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:53.52,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,It was good, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:56.28,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Dot, dot, dot, silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:57.58,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Huh? Did you see it, Aoi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:59.91,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,We don't really watch \Nmuch TV at my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:00.95,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:05.27,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,To be honest, I hardly saw any of the first \Ntwo seasons of {\i1}Tesagure! Bukatsumono.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.27,0:03:08.22,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,What?! Y-You don't check \Nhow it looked on the air?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:12.08,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,The fans at an event had to tell me \Nwhat my "That's new!" pose was.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:15.76,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,I'm impressed you're willing \Nto admit that in a public place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:17.67,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,That's Aoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:20.94,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,How old were you when you first \Nwent to a movie theater?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:23.84,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,I think I was in elementary school...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:26.42,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,The first movie I saw was animated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:29.28,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,I've never been to a movie theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:30.14,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:33.71,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,We have a theater room in our house, \Nso there's no point in going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:34.83,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.83,0:03:37.94,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd see someone \Nbrag about never going to one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:40.35,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,The atmosphere in a movie \Ntheater is pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:41.53,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:45.82,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,It seems much more enjoyable to me \Nto appreciate film sitting alone quietly,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:47.83,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,with no one to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:50.73,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I know what you mean! \NI go see movies alone, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:53.50,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I aim for those times during the week \Nwhen there aren't many people!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:55.37,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Just don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.37,0:03:57.94,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I go see movies alone because I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:03:59.76,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Don't misunderstand that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:02.33,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Okay, okay! You've made your point!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:05.55,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,There are situations where people \Nhold hands at movie theaters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:06.62,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Like on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:10.67,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Isn't that unbelievable? It makes \Nyou think, "Just focus on the movie!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:12.52,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Well, it depends on the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:15.66,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,When I go to see movies with Rin-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:18.66,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,it's become normal for us to \Nhold hands while watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:23.21,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Rin-chan is quick to grab my hand, \Nno matter what the genre is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:24.07,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:26.74,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "huh"? \NYou don't realize you're doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:31.87,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,I bet holding hands in a movie theater \Nis a situation Koharun would like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:34.24,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,True! I'm sure she'd love a date like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.24,0:04:37.95,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,That sounds great! My heart would be throbbing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:40.42,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,I bet you'd emit a sparkle \Neffect even in a theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:43.60,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,But if possible, I wouldn't \Nwant to just hold hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:46.51,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,I'd like to do "helping hands" \Nwith a hot guy while I watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:49.48,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Huh? Your boyfriend wouldn't \Nbe able to see the movie then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:52.31,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,You're the kind of viewer who's \Nmost annoying to others...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:55.25,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,I know! Let's all go see a \Nmovie together sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:56.48,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,A-All of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:59.47,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,I suppose it'd be nice to keep company \Nwith common folk once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:01.86,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,You say "once in a while," \Nbut you always show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:03.53,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Is there anything you want to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:07.81,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Horror, hands down! I want \Nto watch all of you scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.81,0:05:09.83,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,No, keep your eyes on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:11.81,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,I wonder if it'll be empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:14.25,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,It's a weekday, but this is Ladies' Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:15.13,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,1,000 yen, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:15.90,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:19.52,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Kanon-chan, you always get to watch for \N1,000 yen, regardless of the day, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:20.27,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:22.88,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,There are several options,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:25.55,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,but in the end, we couldn't \Ndecide on which one to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:28.05,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,So should we go with the scary one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:31.06,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,I came here intending to cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.84,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,You'll bawl your eyes out if it's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:35.89,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Not that kind of crying. \NI meant like a romance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:39.23,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Either way, isn't it a bit\Nunproductive to pay good money
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:41.75,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,only to get scared or feel sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:44.00,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,What do you usually watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.80,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,I bought popcorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:49.32,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,That's huge! Can you eat all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:50.50,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:53.99,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,It's so puffy, it's like most of it is air.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:55.78,Main Dialogue,Rin,0,0,0,,It's gotta be corn-flavored air.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:57.83,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,No, that's actual corn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:02.98,Italics Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,What should I do? I'm going to cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:04.48,Italics Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:06.67,Italics Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Rin-chan is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:10.49,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:13.74,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,It's good to cry now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:17.60,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Yeah. But you cried too much, Tomomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:19.69,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Well, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:24.86,Italics Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:29.28,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Okay, let's try to think of a "new movie theater."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:29.90,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:30.43,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:30.43,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:31.99,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Okay. Does anyone have an idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:32.49,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.87,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,Okay, Hina-chan's "new movie theater."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:36.78,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,You often hear "also playing now," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:37.37,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:42.63,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,So the screen would be split, \Nwith two movies shown, one on each side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:43.89,Main Dialogue,Yui,0,0,0,,What about the sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:43.89,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,That'd be hard to watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:45.60,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,The sound would be left and right, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:46.85,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,That would be hard to watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:47.59,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:49.37,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,And if there were couples' seats, it'd be like,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:51.46,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,"I'm gonna watch the right screen."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:52.38,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Oh, so afterward...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:52.95,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,"Okay, I'll watch the left."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:54.72,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,They'd share their opinions on them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:54.72,Main Dialogue,Hina,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:56.12,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,How can they share anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:06:59.14,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.65,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Like, "Oh, so that's what it was about."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:02.15,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Yeah. It'd just be an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:04.04,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,It'd be like they didn't even go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:04.76,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:06.57,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Well, if they both want to see the same one...
