Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:31.21,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Click, click.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:35.11,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,You're so happy about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.36,0:12:37.46,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,I have to get the crucial moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:41.05,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Don't look so smug!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:42.72,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,My hands are shaking the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:44.25,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,You're shaking the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:45.82,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,The one in front...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:49.12,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,The one in front keeps looking over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:52.44,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,They froze in that position for, like, 15 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:54.19,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,My data folder is full of meerkats.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:55.02,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,I never get tired of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:55.02,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:56.00,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.35,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:12:58.62,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Hiina-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:12:59.10,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,A little more, a little more this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:00.20,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Please look this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:01.02,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,"Please look this way"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:02.71,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,Hiina-senpai, please send that to me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:05.09,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Sure. The lovers' quarrel pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:09.66,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Just hearing Hiina say "lovers' quarrel"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:11.37,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,The one in front...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:12.19,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,The one in front...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:12.85,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,The one in front...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:14.61,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,It won't go in...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:17.54,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,It won't go in, so it's getting annoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:19.85,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,That was funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.85,0:13:21.48,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,I took a ton of pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:23.39,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,We got more excited about that than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:26.14,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Self-restraint. You need self-restraint.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:26.14,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,If we're like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:29.45,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,"Self-restraint"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:33.45,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Huh? Just you, Tomomi-san? \NWhere's everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:37.53,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Nobody else could make it, \Nso they wanted the two of us to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:38.71,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:43.90,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I guess they thought that by having two polar opposite characters like us go one-on-one,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:46.89,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,they expected to see some \Nunique sense of distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:49.04,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,or some kind of chemical reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.18,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,That makes this hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:56.73,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,What do you say we thoroughly relish this\Nchallenge on our own, comrade Aoi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:57.90,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Tomomi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:58.28,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:13:59.81,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Comrade Tomomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:00.72,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:03.23,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,First, what do you mean by "comrade"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:09.87,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Um, by "comrade," I meant we \Nshare the same objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:10.70,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.70,Main Dialogue,Tomodachi,0,0,0,,Yes. You know what "objective" means?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:17.96,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,"Objective" is... the moment \Nwhen two hearts overlap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:21.97,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Um, wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:23.46,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,And I embarrassed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:25.59,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Is Tomomi-san okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:28.73,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,But "comrade" is a little hard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:30.97,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Do you know what "objective" means?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:33.31,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,It's like, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:34.49,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:35.89,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Will. Consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.27,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Consciousness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:37.52,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:38.31,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Consciousness is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:40.30,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Enthusiasm! Energy! Consciousness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:41.27,Enthusiasm Sign,Yua,0,0,0,,Enthusiasm! Energy! Consciousness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:41.27,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:42.87,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,If you don't have consciousness, you're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:43.88,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,That's important!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:45.11,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:48.28,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,If you don't have consciousness, \Nyour eyes would roll back in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:50.20,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,No! They can't roll back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:52.47,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:58.09,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,This time, we're thinking of a "new zoo," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:57.57,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,A zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:15:00.71,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll give you one of my usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:00.71,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Your usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:04.04,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,My "new zoo."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.62,0:15:09.57,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,There's a place in the petting zoo where \Nyou can grab all the chicks as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:13.64,Petting Zoo Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1)}Grab All the Chicks You Want
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:12.72,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Now that's what I call "a bird in the hand."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:15.77,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Cheep, cheep, cheep...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:17.39,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:17.96,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:19.65,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,I'll say it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:19.64,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,You grab chicks...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:21.92,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,That's what I call "a bird in the hand"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:23.67,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Cheep, cheep, cheep...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:23.67,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,That's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:26.02,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,It doesn't have to be a chick, then, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:26.93,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:30.95,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Right? You should include other types. \NThey're all birds of a feather.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:30.95,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Sparrows?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:31.57,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Sparrows?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:33.70,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Good one! "Birds of a feather."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:34.16,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:34.50,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Nice one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.99,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,No, no. I didn't mean it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:35.99,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,A pun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:37.40,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,It wasn't meant to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:41.55,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll do my "new zoo."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:42.33,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:45.88,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,All of the animals have really loveless names.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:51.27,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,For example, one giraffe's \Nname plate says "AAAA."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:55.85,Giraffe Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,AAAA-kun\NMale, 4 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:53.39,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,And hamsters are referred to as
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:55.19,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,number one, number two, number three...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:55.85,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:57.90,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,They're all... How can I explain it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:16:00.88,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,They're raised under a Soviet-style system.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:02.44,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Poor things!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:03.65,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:05.69,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:06.11,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Those poor things!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:09.14,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,That's true. We need to take good care of animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:10.27,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Animals are a treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:12.77,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,But you were the one talking \Nabout grabbing chicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:14.72,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,That's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:17.69,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,That's fine, but it's no good if \Nthere's no love in their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.69,0:16:18.95,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Oh, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:19.96,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Tomomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:22.45,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,So you're grabbing chicks with names
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:25.25,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,like Machiko and Kiyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:27.84,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,That's right. They have name tags.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.02,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,The chicks...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.34,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Right. That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:30.71,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:36.69,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,I don't get it anymore. \NIt's like my head just went all fuzzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:39.14,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,I don't really understand what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.57,0:16:41.11,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,No, go ahead. Don't hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:42.60,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Pretend I'm not even here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.37,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,If you're not here, then I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:46.31,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,You can do it like you're talking to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.23,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,You're not the type who talks to herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:47.90,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,That's sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:48.95,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:50.64,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,You don't play with dolls?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:53.96,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Play with dolls? No. Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:56.43,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,You {\i1}do{\i0} do!  Er, you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:58.16,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:16:59.54,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,How do you play with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:01.72,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Um, like... You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:05.18,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,"I just moved here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.18,0:17:06.51,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:08.23,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,"Well, come in for some tea."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:10.13,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,"I brought over some soba..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:10.80,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:13.82,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,What should I do? You're a...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:14.24,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:16.97,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,You're a member of the class's upper-class.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:20.54,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,The strongest race in the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:21.60,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,I'm not strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:23.23,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,After all, school's been fun for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:24.42,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Yes, it's been fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:25.19,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,There, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.24,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,It hasn't been fun for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:28.24,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,It's not fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:29.38,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,You don't have any friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:31.00,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I have friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:31.84,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.40,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.65,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:37.32,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Why do you rub salt in people's wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:40.70,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,That innocent laugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:43.94,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,That's the aura of someone \Nwho's had a happy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:46.31,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,But I'm happy being with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:49.54,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,What kind of reaction is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.59,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I'm just a little embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.81,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,It's not because you were freaked out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.81,0:17:53.82,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:54.38,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:59.35,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,No. I, um, have a weakness \Nfor honest words like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:00.83,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Aoi was a little nervous there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:02.08,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Wow, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:04.02,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,The "What am I saying? I don't get it anymore."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:05.56,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,She's not always like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:07.50,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Even when she doesn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:10.12,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,She just blasts through it with more puns.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:12.72,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,But if you play with dolls...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:14.90,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Does that make you part of the lower-class?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.33,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Because you play alone, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:19.28,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,I used to play with dolls all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:18.78,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:21.45,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,How did you play with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:27.94,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,I'd put tons of finger puppets in a box and \Nline them up like a school classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:29.91,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Then if I looked at the inside of the lid,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:32.95,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,all the puppets' names were written there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:34.72,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was like an attendance record.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:39.69,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,And then I'd be the teacher and say,\N"Hey, is blah-blah here today?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:43.51,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,And then another finger puppet \Nwould go, "Yes, I'm here."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:44.72,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,You played all those roles?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:45.48,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,30.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:46.64,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,30 roles!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:47.85,Main Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,That sounds lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:48.66,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.64,0:18:52.82,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,But I was a happy kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:58.45,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Okay, let's continue with your "new zoo."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:18:58.45,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:19:02.02,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,The zookeepers throw dung.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:05.32,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,The zookeepers throw dung.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:08.08,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,So you're like, "{\i1}You're{\i0} throwing it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:12.31,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,So... The zookeepers throw dung
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:17.17,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,because they hate society? \NThat's why they throw dung?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:21.58,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Tomomi-san, um, can I say \Nsomething really terrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:22.09,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:24.97,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,You try really hard to explain what I say,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:27.77,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,but what I say doesn't \Nreally have any meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:28.52,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,It doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:30.52,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,No. It's nothing deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.81,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,It's all surface. I'm shallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:32.81,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,All surface?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:34.55,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,But let's think about the details,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:36.87,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,as long as we're coming up with new zoos...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.87,0:19:41.13,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,For example, if I say, \N"The zookeepers throw dung,"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:43.32,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,all you have to say is, \N"Dung?! That's disgusting!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:47.11,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,But... But they're throwing dung.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:48.70,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Isn't that abnormal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:50.60,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,That's new.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:51.86,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Let's go into that a little deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:55.21,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Why did the zookeepers start throwing dung?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:19:58.03,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Because it was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:19:58.79,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,That's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:00.39,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,"Ah, dung!" Fling!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:01.90,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Oh, jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:02.61,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:05.52,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,If Japan were like that, it'd be doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:06.91,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:11.08,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,If there's a person who would \Nthrow dung because it's there,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:12.48,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,then Japan is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:14.15,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Okay, now for a pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:14.94,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,So suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:17.77,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,"Ew, there's dung on the ground."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:19.05,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,"Crap."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:24.37,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Don't laugh away from the mic!\NGet closer to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:25.76,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:28.83,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Just... What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:33.21,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Why... Why do you say crazy things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:36.63,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Exactly. That's why you should \Njust sort of brush it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:38.50,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I see... Okay. Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:39.76,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.39,0:20:40.76,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Because it's dung.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:44.90,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Argh, so frustrating! This is so frustrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.89,0:20:42.96,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Okay, let's move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:46.06,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0,0,0,,Let's move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:47.05,Main Dialogue,Tomomi,0,0,0,,That's so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:52.58,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0,0,0,,Aoi just confessed to being "all surface."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:54.17,Main Dialogue,Yua,0,0,0,,She said it about herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:55.48,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's gotta hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:57.15,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0,0,0,,That's the best shot.
