Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.22,0:22:30.57,Main Dialogue,Mobuko,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:32.76,Main Dialogue,Mobue,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to push each other like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.76,0:22:34.24,Main Dialogue,Mobudai,0,0,0,,What's that light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:35.37,Main Dialogue,Grandmob,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:38.62,Main Dialogue,King,0,0,0,,Mobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:41.39,Main Dialogue,Grandmob,0,0,0,,Legend has it that when the \Nsleeping demon king wakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.39,0:22:44.84,Main Dialogue,Grandmob,0,0,0,,Mobuko will appear as a king who \Ntranscends time and space.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:47.17,Main Dialogue,Grandmob,0,0,0,,But I never thought \NKing Mobuko really would appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.17,0:22:48.74,Main Dialogue,Mobuko,0,0,0,,King Mobuko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.74,0:22:50.21,Main Dialogue,Mobuka,0,0,0,,Not "queen"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.21,0:22:52.43,Main Dialogue,Dr. Mobu,0,0,0,,It must be a side effect of the time travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:22:55.35,Main Dialogue,Mobue,0,0,0,,Maybe he can defeat Mobustopheles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.35,0:22:56.34,Main Dialogue,Mobuko,0,0,0,,Yeah, maybe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:58.02,Main Dialogue,King,0,0,0,,Mobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.02,0:22:59.38,Main Dialogue,Voice,0,0,0,,See you next week!
